WEBVTT

00:01.294 --> 00:04.422
AKU: Long ago,
in a distant land,

00:04.506 --> 00:09.260
I, Aku, the shape-shifting
master of darkness,

00:09.344 --> 00:13.014
unleashed an unspeakable evil.

00:13.097 --> 00:18.686
But, a foolish Samurai warrior
wielding a magic sword,

00:18.770 --> 00:21.523
stepped forth to oppose me.

00:22.315 --> 00:24.108
