19:37.719 --> 19:38.762
It's a baby.

19:40.180 --> 19:41.556
A baby dragon.

19:47.145 --> 19:50.065
DRAGON: Please hurry.

19:50.190 --> 19:53.527
I cannot stand much more.

20:27.936 --> 20:30.021
DRAGON: Thank you.

20:38.947 --> 20:39.948
(SQUEAKING)

20:51.543 --> 20:52.544
Look.

20:54.045 --> 20:55.630
TOWNSPEOPLE: Huzzah!

20:56.339 --> 20:58.759
(CHEERING)

21:02.220 --> 21:04.556
Well, I gotta hand it to you, robed one,

21:04.639 --> 21:07.142
I never thought you'd get rid
of that stench.

21:07.350 --> 21:09.519
